>> DEPRECATED — do not import from this file.
>>
>> This file used to re-export assert.mld + runner.mld as a convenience.
>> It was removed because importing from here is a footgun: when your test
>> exes call @assertOk AND you pass them to @runSuites, the static
>> circular-reference detector flags a false-positive cycle through the
>> re-export chain.
>>
>> Import directly instead:
>>   import { @assertOk, @assertEq } from "./assert.mld"
>>   import { @suite, @group, @runSuites } from "./runner.mld"
